        <p>Scan or upload the image then use the edit tools to crop and rotate. When finished click the &acute;Save&acute; button to attach the image to the Application.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="avgrund-close hint--left" data-hint="Close" onclick="javascript:closeDialog();"></div> <!-- Close button -->
        </div>
        <div id="second-popup" class="avgrund-popup">
        <h2>That's a completely different popup</h2>
        <p>
        You can hit ESC or click outside to close the modal. Give it a go to see the reverse transition.
        </p>
        <button onclick="javascript:closeDialog();">Close</button>
